:35:53.000Z","msg":"除了央視，其他内地的電視台内容還是經過審查，只是有綫電視過去一直都會集中播放比較負面的内容，不會主動歌頌政府，而且有綫還會自己派員到内地做偵查報道，水平當然比現在被動轉發央視片段好得多。<br />\n另外，他們如果一味唱好，或者只播放軟性内容，那他們和CCTVB的支那掠影有什麽分別？就算是支持共產黨的垃圾Nancy，也寧願看鳳凰衛視。"},{"pid":"b3d02a040768caaff40e73fb13d2fc945dc87c11","tid":2350714,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"新班底叫唱好支那咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b74c1474440bef90ec932770abc295fb109fff","tid":2350714,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d02a040768caaff40e73fb13d2fc945dc87c11","tid":2350714,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"新班底叫唱好支那咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"解放軍50 人能攻陷白宮"},{"pid":"f695a6856f64c80f1ee2dc7cd00095e4ae164eaa","tid":2350714,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6b74c1474440bef90ec932770abc295fb109fff","tid":2350714,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3d02a040768caaff40e73fb13d2fc945dc87c11","tid":2350714,"uid":192997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:38:59.000Z","msg":"新班底叫唱好支那咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"解放軍50 人能攻陷白宮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nin習帝"},{"pid":"487ba38e149ea917b9c392d891032a6abb7030aa","tid":2350714,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"我要睇呢啲睇CCTV都得啦，仲洗睇你有線咩"},{"pid":"8b0769ee7bb16d21b7549ba4a413e562b45edea6","tid":2350714,"uid":114781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2